    <JadeMethod name="processSAPDataKinerja" id="49d7cab3-3f36-4fd4-a104-18029df17ed5">
        <updating/>
        <source>processSAPDataKinerja(_agent : CM_SAPWSConsumerAgent input) : Boolean updating ,protected;

/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason
04 Sep 2018 cnwma1	ChangeRequest 38638: PEL1 - SAP Send Performance (Kinerja) Data
27 Oct 2018 jlger1  tfs 41625 -  have tasks for each terminal
17 Dec 2018	cnwma1	ChangeRequest 38638: PEL1 - SAP Send Performance (Kinerja) Data
